A cyberpunk cityscape at night featuring multiple towering server monoliths connected by glowing neon data streams forming a web pattern between them. In the foreground, a single luminous document hologram floats, encased in a geometric cage of pulsing electric blue and magenta lock barriers. The barriers extend as thin laser lines to each server tower, creating a triangular mesh of protection. Rain falls through the scene, refracting the neon lights. The servers have visible circuitry patterns glowing beneath dark metallic surfaces, and small drones hover near each tower like digital sentinels. The atmosphere is moody with deep purple shadows and electric cyan highlights, conveying coordination and security across a distributed network.
